        crm:P2_has_type               <urn:uuid:786a6773-3c30-4d75-967e-3dd5aad44c2f> ;
        crm:P3_has_note               "Multi-user collaborative VR environment, developed in Unity and accessed via Meta Quest 3 headsets. Supports synchronous multi-user sessions with avatar-based interaction. In the Vallombrosa pilot, extends single-user VR exploration (navigation, sensor placement, AI-assisted querying) with multi-user networking (Netcode). In the Caldana pilot, used to generate input JSON payloads for simulation microservices interactively, enabling collaborative scenario configuration." ;
